# Default Event Poster Placeholder

This file should be replaced with an actual event poster image named `default-event-poster.jpg`.

Recommended specifications:
- Format: JPG or PNG
- Resolution: 1920x1080 (16:9 aspect ratio) or higher
- File size: Under 2MB for optimal loading
- Content: Event branding, competition name, date, etc.

The image will be used as the background for the judge landing page when no specific event poster is configured.